Switch Plugin Version 0.1
-------------------------

This plugin enables per node theme/layout switching

Configuration
-------------

1. Activate the plugin

2. Create or edit a new Node/Blog/Page and choose the theme/layout in
   the Switcher tab

Requirements
------------

Croogo - http://croogo.org/

At this point, this requires custom changes that has not been accepted upstream.
Get the required changes from: git://github.com/rchavik/croogo/1.4-rchavik.
Note that this branch could be unstable and subject to rebase/rewind.

Table `nodes` needs be altered to add `params` field.

``
	alter table nodes add `params` text after created;
``

You have been warned.

Still,..
Good luck and have fun.

-- rchavik
